OL,3,CMan jailed for stabbing pregnant ex-
OL,4,Cgirlfriend in Aberfan
OL,6,FA 29-year-old man has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto more than 17 years in prison after
OL,8,Frepeatedly stabbing his pregnant ex-
OL,9,Fgirlfriend.
OL,11,FDaniel Popescu, of no fixed abode,
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to attempting to murder
OL,13,FAndreea Pintili in , in , on December
OL,14,F5 last year.
OL,16,FHe also admitted to a stalking offence
OL,17,Fbut denied a further charge of
OL,18,Fintimidation, a charge the Crown
OL,19,FProsecution Service (CPS) decided not
OL,20,Fto pursue given the guilty attempted
OL,21,Fmurder plea.
