OL,6,FCrown Court heard how Popescu and Miss
OL,7,FPintili had split up around August
OL,8,F2023 after Popescu developed a
OL,9,Fgambling habit. He then became
OL,10,Fobsessed with her.
OL,12,FOn the day of the attack, was brought
OL,13,Fto a standstill with schools locked
OL,14,Fdown while armed police searched for
OL,15,Fthe knifeman who had fled the scene.
