OL,6,FFootage played in court showed a
OL,7,Fhooded Popescu crouching behind a
OL,8,Fvehicle with a seven to eight-inch
OL,9,Fknife in his hand as he waited for
OL,10,FMiss Pintili to return home from
OL,11,Ftaking her children to school.
OL,13,FIt then showed Popescu grab Miss
OL,14,FPintili by the arm, at which point she
OL,15,Fattempted to run away but fell to the
OL,16,Fground. Popescu then stabbed her a
OL,17,Fnumber of times.
