OL,6,FMiss Pintili, who was 37 weeks
OL,7,Fpregnant at the time, described
OL,8,Fholding her stomach and trying to
OL,9,Fprotect her unborn child.
OL,11,FA woman who had been passing with her
OL,12,Fdog screamed and ran to try and help,
OL,13,Fwhich caused Popescu to run off.
OL,15,FMiss Pintili was taken to the
OL,16,FUniversity Hospital of Wales in
OL,17,FCardiff with stab wounds to her back
OL,18,Fand thumb.
