OL,6,FDescribing the attack, she said:
OL,7,F"Popescu tried to get me into my
OL,8,Fhouse, he told me he had a knife and
OL,9,Fto get in the house.
OL,11,F"I have no doubt that had he got me
OL,12,Finto the house he would've killed me.
OL,13,FThis was clearly his intention that
OL,14,Fday, to kill me and my unborn child.
OL,16,F"I still feel very anxious about what
OL,17,FPopescu did to me and I have sleepless
OL,18,Fnights and nightmares just thinking
OL,19,Fabout it.
