OL,6,F"Since the attack, if I feel something
OL,7,Ftouch my back I tremble in fear. I
OL,8,Falways keep all of my doors and
OL,9,Fwindows locked for safety and I was
OL,10,Fnever like this prior to the attack.
OL,12,F"I feel I will never be safe from this
OL,13,Fman. I feel very scared and anxious of
OL,14,Fthe thought of him being released."
