OL,6,FProsecuting, John Hipkin KC told the
OL,7,Fcourt how in the weeks leading up to
OL,8,Fthe attack, Popescu had repeatedly
OL,9,Fknocked on the window of Miss
OL,10,FPintili's previous address, left bags
OL,11,Fof his clothes outside her house,
OL,12,Fphoned her multiple times and left her
OL,13,Fvoicemails saying he would not leave
OL,14,Fher street until she got back together
OL,15,Fwith him.
OL,17,FPopescu was consequently arrested and
OL,18,Freleased on bail and told not to
OL,19,Fcontact Miss Pintili.
