OL,6,FThese events led Miss Pintili to move
OL,7,Fto , but in late November 2023 she saw
OL,8,FPopescu near her new address.
OL,10,FThe court heard how Popescu sent a
OL,11,Fnumber of messages to his sister in
OL,12,FRomania, saying "Andreea got back with
OL,13,Fher ex, I haven't been in work for a
OL,14,Fweek, I've been following them every
OL,15,Fday, and today I found out where it
OL,16,Fis".
