OL,6,FHe also sent two further messages to
OL,7,Fhis sister, saying "yes, wh***s must
OL,8,Fdie, why should they put my son under
OL,9,Fhis name? Not once in a lifetime will
OL,10,Fthat ever happen", and that he would
OL,11,F"either go to jail or kill myself if I
OL,12,Fcan", which prosecutors said revealed
OL,13,Fthat the attack was pre-planned.
OL,15,FPopescu had been seen leaving the
OL,16,Fhouse he was staying in at the time
OL,17,Fbetween 4am and 5am every day to look
OL,18,Ffor Miss Pintili's new partner.
