OL,6,FDefending, David Aubrey KC highlighted
OL,7,Fhow Popescu has no previous
OL,8,Fconvictions, was sleeping rough at the
OL,9,Ftime, and there were concerns about
OL,10,Fhim taking his own life.
OL,12,FHe said Popescu has expressed "genuine
OL,13,Fremorse and regret".
OL,15,FBut sentencing, Judge Tracey Lloyd-
OL,16,FClarke said the aggravating factors
OL,17,Foutweighed the mitigating factors.
