OL,6,FShe imposed an extended sentence
OL,7,Fcomprised of 17 years and four months
OL,8,Fin prison - with at least two thirds
OL,9,Fto be served in custody before Popescu
OL,10,Fcan be considered for parole - and a
OL,11,Ffurther three years on licence.
OL,13,FAn indefinite restraining order was
OL,14,Falso placed on the defendant, who has
OL,15,Fbeen served with notices of
OL,16,Fdeportation back to Romania.
OL,18,FPopescu wept in the dock as he was
OL,19,Fsentenced.
