OL,6,FDetective Inspector James Morris, from
OL,7,F, said: "Daniel Popescu armed himself
OL,8,Fwith a knife and lay in wait for his
OL,9,Fvictim before launching a senseless
OL,10,Fand sustained act of violence in the
OL,11,Fmiddle of the street.
OL,13,F"I can only imagine the fear she must
OL,14,Fhave felt and the impact this
OL,15,Fdisturbing incident has had on her.
OL,17,F"It is clear from the sheer vicious
OL,18,Fand sustained force he used that his
OL,19,Fintention was to kill her.
