OL,6,F"The strength and bravery of the
OL,7,Fvictim in supporting this prosecution
OL,8,Fhas been extraordinary.
OL,10,F"Unsurprisingly she remains
OL,11,Fpsychologically scarred as a result of
OL,12,Fthe incident, but I know that, thanks
OL,13,Fto her courage, Daniel Popescu will be
OL,14,Funable to harm any further women. I
OL,15,Fhope that today's sentence will bring
OL,16,Fat least a degree of closure for her.
OL,18,F"I must also commend the actions of
OL,19,Fthe courageous member of the public
OL,20,Ffor their bravery in running to help
OL,21,Fthe victim after the attack."
