OL,6,FJordan Jones, senior crown prosecutor
OL,7,Fat CPS Cymru-Wales, said: "This was an
OL,8,Funprovoked, vicious attack that had a
OL,9,Fgreat effect on not only the victim,
OL,10,Fbut the wider community as local
OL,11,Fschools were forced into shut down
OL,12,Funtil the police were able to detain
OL,13,Fthe defendant shortly after the attack.
OL,15,F"I hope the sentencing of this
OL,16,Fdefendant brings a sense of justice to
OL,17,Fboth the victim and the wider
OL,18,Fcommunity affected by the defendant's
OL,19,Factions."
